title: Personalized Guitar Pick Keychain
description: This listing includes a 1 1/4" x 1" personalized copper guitar pick, oxidized to give it a beautiful rustic look.. Also included is a custom leather pick case to store your treasured item in. Your purchase will arrive in an organza bag nestled inside a lovely cotton filled gift box wrapped with beautiful ribbon ready for gift giving! This is a beautiful personalized custom rustic copper guitar pick for that special someone in your life! Father of the Bride/Dad, anniversary gift, Christmas gift, or simply to make him smile. This is the perfect keepsake gift! Since the pick is 24 gauge it can actually be used to play, or simply be kept as a keepsake for that special someone. I can add initials or a date at the bottom, or we can change the saying to something else of your choice.
